MAKE MONEY!!!!!<br>
<br>
HIRING SNOW BLOWER OPERATORS-SHOVELERS <br>
 Professional landscape and snow plowing company is seeking snow blower operators/shovelers.<br>
<br>
 USE OUR EQUIPMENT!!! MAKE BIG DOLLARS WHEN IT SNOWS!!!<br>
<br>
 CALL 708.301.8396 OR TEXT 708.878.5717<br>
<br>
Shop Address:<br>
 15836 Annico Drive<br>
 Homer Glen, IL.<br>
 Off 159th between Bell and Parker - between the two Danrich Automotive buildings!<br>
<br>
<br>
 Office: Seven Zero Eight 3 0 1 . 8 3 9 6<br>
Cell. Seven Zero Eight 8 7 8 . 5 7 1 7 (Text)<br>
<br>
 We are hiring snow blower operators/shovelers to use our snow blowers for clearing sidewalks/residential driveways. Great opportunity to earn money during the winter. We are looking for reliable, hardworking, detail oriented people to snow blow/shovel during the winter time. We have reliable, newer equipment. We have a variety of routes available from Zero-tolerance/salting to 1" or 2" routes. We prefer to assign routes to individuals that prove they will be reliable for every snow event needed and on time.<br>
<br>
 GREAT COMMUNICATION and we try to provide ample notice unlike the others that call at a moments notice.<br>
<br>
 Snow Blower Operators/Shovelers must have the following:<br>
 - Must have 24/7 availability<br>
 - Must be Available from 11/15/2016 - 4/15/2017<br>
 - Experience with snow blowers a plus/Actual shovel work required<br>
 - Must have reliable communication (cell phone/schedule updates are often texted)<br>
 - Must have reliable transportation (public transportation not avail. during middle of night)<br>
 - Must be able to follow instructions<br>
 - Must have winter gear (warm boots/hats/gloves/jackets)<br>
 - Must be able to work outdoors in the elements.<br>
 - Must be able to fill out company paper work properly<br>
 - Must be hard working and responsible<br>
 - Must be able to lift 50# - 75# regularly<br>
 - MUST BE ABLE TO WORK LONG HOURS<br>
<br>
 ***EXTRA PAY FOR BRINGING A VEHICLE THAT CAN TRANSPORT 3 - 5 MAN CREW, SNOW BLOWERS, SHOVELS, AND GAS CANS.***<br>
<br>
 ***EXTRA PAY IF YOU PUT TOGETHER YOUR OWN 2 - 5 MAN CREW***<br>
<br>
 Pay Starting at $15.00 - $18.00 per hour.<br>
Extra $1.00/hr if you bring someone to work<br>
<br>
 ONLY SERIOUS APPLICANTS APPLY!!!<br>
<br>
 CALL FOR DETAILS!!!<br>
<br>
 Please respond via email or Text<br>
 We are hiring immediately.<br>
 <br>
 15836 Annico Drive<br>
 Homer Glen, IL 60491<br>
 M- TH. Between 9am and 4pm<br>
<br>
 We are located:<br>
 - 4 miles east of I355 off of 159th Street (just east of Aspen Valley Landscape Supply)<br>
 - 4.3 miles west of La Grange road off of 159th Street (2 blocks west of bell road)<br>
<br>
 (SPECIAL CONSIDERATION GIVEN TO CURRENT/FORMER U.S. MILITARY PERSONEL)<br>
<br>
 WINTER WORK<br>
 WINTER<br>
 SNOW<br>
 SNOW SHOVEL<br>
 SHOVEL<br>
 SNOW LABOR<br>
 SNOW BLOWER<br>
 LABORER<br>
 LABOR<br>
 PART-TIME<br>
 SEASONAL<br>
 ROOFERS<br>
 SIDING<br>
 POWER WASHING    </section>

